{"Title":"迟菜心炒肉的做法","Primary":["油菜苔500克","猪肉(瘦)100克"],"Auxiliary":["油适量","盐1茶匙","白糖0.5茶匙","味极鲜1茶匙","蚝油1茶匙","姜蒜15克"],"Flavoring":[],"Setups":["1.把菜心洗净","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267432228314.jpg","2.用手直接掰成段，把茎与叶分开","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267436304099.jpg","3.瘦肉切片后，加入适量的盐，糖，味极鲜，生粉，食用油腌制","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267438181477.jpg","4.姜蒜切片备用","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267440330853.jpg","5.锅烧热，把肉片放入滑炒至断生，然后盛出备用","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267441147788.jpg","6.翻炒留底油，把蒜姜片放入爆香","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267442276547.jpg","7.接着放入菜心梗翻炒至断生","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267443596779.jpg","8.然后加入菜心叶翻炒","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267444774598.jpg","9.放入适量的盐与糖","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267445844058.jpg","10.少来一点蚝油提鲜","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267447029807.jpg","11.然后把肉片放入锅内翻炒","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267448791852.jpg","12.大火炒匀","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267450825953.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267431822013.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267433565623.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267435687772.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267437961063.jpg","烹饪技巧","瘦肉在炒制前最好用少许的盐，糖，生粉，食用油腌制一下，这样的肉片口感更滑嫩哦。"]}